57.movie_plot: A woman rebels against a tyrannical ruler in postapocalyptic Australia in search for her home-land with the help of a group of female prisoners, a psychotic worshipper, and a drifter named Max.

109.movie_plot: A prospector goes to the Klondike in search of gold and finds it and more.

107.movie_plot: The staff of an army hospital in the Korean war find that laughter is the best way to deal with their situation.
